page.title: 10INDUSTRIAL ESTATE
page.content: Some of the firms are-Novomec a flower and plant company.It has some big greenhouses in Norfolk where they grow flowers and plants for shops.Hardy marine deals in boats.Lamco is a sweet and soft drink warehouse it is just like a cash and carry.The lavender laundry in{North Walsham }started in 1977 but before that it was called {North walsham steam laundry it started in 1901.The laundry hires all differnt clothes.North Walsham glass company make and repear windows. And there is a ready mixed concrete firm (Ennemix). There is also a Vauxhall garage where they keep brand new cars.{R&D Pennants make flags and flag poles stickers for the back of cars ETC. { Coda plastics}make cosmetics lids etc. by injecion moulding.
